file_browser.delete_project.one_file_con.string: Project {folderName} and one file will be deleted. The project will be permanently deleted, but you can restore files from the 'Deleted' tab in your drafts.

file_browser.delete_project.plural_files.string: Project {folderName} and all {numFiles} of its files will be deleted. The project will be permanently deleted, but you can restore files from the 'Deleted' tab in your drafts.

file_browser.api_folder.error_when_delet.string: An error occurred when deleting this project.

memory_warning_modal.memory_reduction_ti.string: Break up bigger files into smaller ones.
Move a few pages to a new file, or split a large library into smaller ones.
Delete hidden layers you don’t need and reduce nested layers, especially in components.
Flatten complex SVGs and vector shapes.
This reduces layers, and therefore memory use.
Trim the number of component variants.
Replace variants with component properties instead.

manage_memory_modal.show_memory_in_layer.string: Showing this might slow down your files.
